    <p>The typical roti dough automation setup involves three stages: kneading (dough kneading machine), portioning (dough divider or manual), and pressing/cooking (roti making machine). The kneading stage is the foundation — if the dough quality is inconsistent, every roti that follows will be inconsistent.</p>

